Analysis of own data

Tuesday 9th ? Classes from 09:30 to 17:30
Day 2
Theory
Ensembles and bagging
Random forests
Learning from mistakes
Practical
Analysis of data with Random Forests:
Supervised learning, training assessing predictive accuracy
